## Output directories

- Plots are written under: \$BIOSEQ_OUTPUT_DIR/example_summary_plots (defaults to ./results/example_summary_plots)
- You can override with BIOSEQ_OUTPUT_DIR or pass absolute paths to save_plot functions.
